name: WoodenPunks #1
description:
The First Punk to be Woodenized! WoodenPunks #1 is a three piece NFT (2 part digital, 1 part physical) including glb, gif, and a one of a kind WoodenPunks #1 Wood Coaster.

High quality custom wooden coaster for your crypto/ NFT cup of choice.

This WoodenPunk #1 enables the Woodenization of other Punk Characters.
